cs.FL, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with automata and their expressive power. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper discusses the complexity of decision problems for automata. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper deals with quantitative properties and their representation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper discusses the expressive power of automata in representing average response time. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper discusses the limitations of weighted automata and proposes a new subclass of automata.
